{
  "meta": {
    "slug": "eng-quality-engineer-technical-technical-y0ju",
    "category": "pro/engineering/quality_engineer",
    "source_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Y0JUklJdRhg",
    "mode": "srt"
  },
  "dialogue": [
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The button.",
      "zh": "這個鈕扣。",
      "ja": "ボタン。",
      "time": "00:00:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "So what do you think?",
      "zh": "那你覺得怎麼樣？",
      "ja": "それで、どう思う？",
      "time": "00:00:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Did Tom Thomas do a ride on his test?",
      "zh": "湯姆·托馬斯考試作弊了嗎？",
      "ja": "トム・トーマスはテストでカンニングした？",
      "time": "00:00:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Of course he did.",
      "zh": "當然有。",
      "ja": "もちろんだよ。",
      "time": "00:00:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "How cute was there?",
      "zh": "那裡有多可愛？",
      "ja": "そこはどれほどかわいかった？",
      "time": "00:00:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What has he got to do with Kotlin?",
      "zh": "他和Kotlin有什麼關係？",
      "ja": "彼はKotlinと何の関係があるの？",
      "time": "00:00:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hey, Fixies. How's it going?",
      "zh": "嘿，修理小精靈們，近來如何？",
      "ja": "ねえ、フィクシーズ、調子はどう？",
      "time": "00:00:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Great. And how was your test?",
      "zh": "很好。你的考試怎麼樣？",
      "ja": "いいよ。テストはどうだった？",
      "time": "00:00:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Easy peasy.",
      "zh": "輕而易舉。",
      "ja": "簡単だったよ。",
      "time": "00:00:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "If it wasn't for me checking your answers,",
      "zh": "如果不是我幫你檢查答案，",
      "ja": "もし僕が君の答えをチェックしてなかったら、",
      "time": "00:00:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I would have managed myself.",
      "zh": "你自己也能應付。",
      "ja": "君は自分でやれたはずだ。",
      "time": "00:00:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You can't even manage to say thank.",
      "zh": "你連說謝謝都做不到。",
      "ja": "ありがとうも言えないくせに。",
      "time": "00:00:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, what's the big deal? You helped me once.",
      "zh": "喔，有什麼大不了的？你幫過我一次。",
      "ja": "ああ、何がそんなに大事なの？一度だけ助けてくれたじゃないか。",
      "time": "00:00:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And yesterday, who found that mistake on your spelling test?",
      "zh": "昨天是誰發現你拼寫測驗的錯誤？",
      "ja": "昨日は誰が君のスペリングテストの間違いを見つけた？",
      "time": "00:00:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I just didn't have time to check it.",
      "zh": "我只是沒時間檢查。",
      "ja": "ただチェックする時間がなかっただけだ。",
      "time": "00:00:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And when you forgot your phone back at gym class,",
      "zh": "當你在體育課忘了帶手機時，",
      "ja": "体育の授業で携帯を忘れた時、",
      "time": "00:00:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "who brought it to you?",
      "zh": "是誰幫你拿回來的？",
      "ja": "誰が持ってきてくれた？",
      "time": "00:00:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Uh, I...",
      "zh": "呃，我...",
      "ja": "えっと、僕は...",
      "time": "00:00:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And who tells you what homework we have all the time?",
      "zh": "誰一直告訴你我們有什麼作業？",
      "ja": "いつも宿題を教えてくれるのは誰？",
      "time": "00:00:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I could have done all that stuff on myself.",
      "zh": "我自己也能做那些事。",
      "ja": "全部自分でできたよ。",
      "time": "00:00:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I didn't ask it to.",
      "zh": "我沒要求你幫忙。",
      "ja": "頼んでないよ。",
      "time": "00:00:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Huh?",
      "zh": "嗯？",
      "ja": "え？",
      "time": "00:00:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Without me around?",
      "zh": "沒有我在身邊？",
      "ja": "僕がいなかったら？",
      "time": "00:00:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I bet you couldn't even sew this button on.",
      "zh": "我打賭你連這個鈕扣都縫不上。",
      "ja": "このボタンすら縫えないだろうな。",
      "time": "00:00:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm so scared.",
      "zh": "我好害怕。",
      "ja": "怖いよ。",
      "time": "00:00:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Just watch me do it.",
      "zh": "看我怎麼做。",
      "ja": "見ててよ。",
      "time": "00:00:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I dare you.",
      "zh": "我敢打賭。",
      "ja": "賭けてみろよ。",
      "time": "00:01:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Fine.",
      "zh": "好吧。",
      "ja": "いいよ。",
      "time": "00:01:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "In ancient times, people stitched together their clothes with strong knots and kept them closed with sticks and thorns from different plants.",
      "zh": "古代，人們用結實的結把衣服縫合，並用不同植物的棍子和刺固定。",
      "ja": "昔、人々は丈夫な結び目で服を縫い合わせ、様々な植物の棒やとげで閉じていました。",
      "time": "00:01:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "The very first buttons were made out of stone, wood, shells, or gold.",
      "zh": "最早的鈕扣是用石頭、木頭、貝殼或黃金製成的。",
      "ja": "最初のボタンは石、木、貝殻、または金で作られていました。",
      "time": "00:01:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Really just about anything.",
      "zh": "幾乎什麼東西都可以。",
      "ja": "本当に何でも。",
      "time": "00:01:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "There was a time when the number of buttons on someone's clothes would indicate how rich that person was.",
      "zh": "曾經有一段時間，衣服上的鈕扣數量代表一個人的富有程度。",
      "ja": "かつては、服のボタンの数がその人の富の指標でした。",
      "time": "00:01:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "As for the buttons on sleeves, first they were put on uniforms to keep soldiers from wiping their noses and mouths on them.",
      "zh": "袖子上的鈕扣最初是裝在制服上，防止士兵用袖子擦鼻子和嘴巴。",
      "ja": "袖のボタンは最初、兵士が鼻や口を袖で拭くのを防ぐために制服に付けられました。",
      "time": "00:01:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Now we know better than to wipe our mouths on our sleeves, but nevertheless, buttons are still used today throughout the world as both a decoration and as a reliable fastener.",
      "zh": "現在我們知道不該用袖子擦嘴，但鈕扣仍被用作裝飾和可靠的扣件。",
      "ja": "今では袖で口を拭かないことは分かっていますが、それでもボタンは装飾と確実な留め具として世界中で使われています。",
      "time": "00:01:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Sewing on a button isn't very difficult, but it's very important to be careful and work properly with a needle, so you don't hurt yourself.",
      "zh": "縫鈕扣不難，但要小心使用針，避免受傷。",
      "ja": "ボタンを縫うのは難しくありませんが、針を正しく使い、怪我をしないように注意することが大切です。",
      "time": "00:01:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Eh.",
      "zh": "欸。",
      "ja": "ええ。",
      "time": "00:01:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Eh.",
      "zh": "欸。",
      "ja": "ええ。",
      "time": "00:01:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What's going on?",
      "zh": "發生什麼事了？",
      "ja": "どうしたの？",
      "time": "00:01:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Tom Thomas.",
      "zh": "湯姆·托馬斯。",
      "ja": "トム・トーマス。",
      "time": "00:01:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You want me to help you?",
      "zh": "你要我幫忙嗎？",
      "ja": "手伝おうか？",
      "time": "00:02:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yeah, Tom Thomas.",
      "zh": "是的，湯姆·托馬斯。",
      "ja": "うん、トム・トーマス。",
      "time": "00:02:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Need some help there?",
      "zh": "需要幫忙嗎？",
      "ja": "助けが必要？",
      "time": "00:02:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm fine.",
      "zh": "我沒事。",
      "ja": "大丈夫。",
      "time": "00:02:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Teddish.",
      "zh": "泰迪什。",
      "ja": "テディッシュ。",
      "time": "00:02:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You're practically finished, except for sewing the button on.",
      "zh": "你差不多完成了，只剩縫鈕扣。",
      "ja": "ボタンを縫うだけでほぼ終わりだね。",
      "time": "00:02:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You're not into it.",
      "zh": "你不感興趣。",
      "ja": "やる気がないね。",
      "time": "00:02:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What's there to know, Nolik?",
      "zh": "有什麼好學的，諾利克？",
      "ja": "何を学ぶ必要があるんだ、ノリック？",
      "time": "00:02:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Stop!",
      "zh": "停！",
      "ja": "やめて！",
      "time": "00:02:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "How about you try practicing first on this?",
      "zh": "先試著在這個上練習怎麼樣？",
      "ja": "これでまず練習してみたら？",
      "time": "00:02:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Be careful that needle is sharp.",
      "zh": "小心，針很尖。",
      "ja": "針は鋭いから気をつけて。",
      "time": "00:02:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Don't distract me.",
      "zh": "別分心我。",
      "ja": "邪魔しないで。",
      "time": "00:02:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Ow.",
      "zh": "哎呦。",
      "ja": "痛っ。",
      "time": "00:02:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That's what happens when you forget to follow the safety rules.",
      "zh": "忘記遵守安全規則就會這樣。",
      "ja": "安全ルールを守らないとこうなるんだ。",
      "time": "00:02:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Here's the thimble.",
      "zh": "這是頂針。",
      "ja": "これが指ぬきだよ。",
      "time": "00:02:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Know how it works?",
      "zh": "知道怎麼用嗎？",
      "ja": "使い方わかる？",
      "time": "00:02:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I can figure it out.",
      "zh": "我能弄懂。",
      "ja": "わかるよ。",
      "time": "00:02:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "We've got to do something about this.",
      "zh": "我們得想辦法。",
      "ja": "これを何とかしないと。",
      "time": "00:02:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, Katya.",
      "zh": "喔，卡佳。",
      "ja": "ああ、カティア。",
      "time": "00:02:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "One of the buttons on your backpack.",
      "zh": "你背包上的一個鈕扣。",
      "ja": "君のリュックのボタンの一つが。",
      "time": "00:03:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Look, it fell off, see?",
      "zh": "看，它掉了，看到嗎？",
      "ja": "ほら、取れちゃったよ。",
      "time": "00:03:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's just awful.",
      "zh": "真糟糕。",
      "ja": "ひどいね。",
      "time": "00:03:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Tom Thomas.",
      "zh": "湯姆·托馬斯。",
      "ja": "トム・トーマス。",
      "time": "00:03:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Do you have another needle?",
      "zh": "你有其他針嗎？",
      "ja": "他の針はある？",
      "time": "00:03:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "School starts soon.",
      "zh": "學校快開學了。",
      "ja": "もうすぐ学校が始まる。",
      "time": "00:03:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Time to rule.",
      "zh": "該掌控一切了。",
      "ja": "支配の時間だ。",
      "time": "00:03:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Art your shirt has got a hole.",
      "zh": "你的襯衫有個洞。",
      "ja": "シャツに穴が開いてるよ。",
      "time": "00:03:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Don't waste time.",
      "zh": "別浪費時間。",
      "ja": "時間を無駄にしないで。",
      "time": "00:03:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "All upset.",
      "zh": "別難過。",
      "ja": "落ち込まないで。",
      "time": "00:03:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You can admit that hole no sweat.",
      "zh": "你可以承認那個洞沒什麼大不了。",
      "ja": "その穴は大したことないって認めなよ。",
      "time": "00:03:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Stop your moaning.",
      "zh": "別抱怨了。",
      "ja": "愚痴はやめて。",
      "time": "00:03:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Do not out.",
      "zh": "別放棄。",
      "ja": "諦めないで。",
      "time": "00:03:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "With some patience, there's no doubt.",
      "zh": "有點耐心，沒問題。",
      "ja": "少しの忍耐で、間違いない。",
      "time": "00:03:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That a needle and some thread will help you out.",
      "zh": "針和線會幫助你的。",
      "ja": "針と糸が助けてくれるよ。",
      "time": "00:03:45"
    }
  ]
}